        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ajcs-conjecture"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#ajcs-conjecture">#</a> Ajc’s Conjecture</h1><p>A 先生在尺规作图时发现:</p><blockquote><p>AH 为 AJ 和 AK 的平分线，过任意点 D 作 DL、DK, 交点如图。连接 IJ、GH 交于 N,HL、IK 交于 M. 则<strong> D、N、M</strong> 共线。<br><img data-src="https://www.helloimg.com/images/2023/05/02/oqcGIK.png" alt="" width="500px"></p></blockquote><p>之后经过推广和相应的作图验证发现不仅平分线满足如上性质，总结提出了<strong> Ajc’s Conjecture</strong>:</p><div class="note info"><p>平面内 AB、AE、AC 共点，DF、DC 共点，交点如图。连接 GE 和 BH，FE 和 HC 分别交于点 M、N，则<strong> D、M、N</strong> 共线。<br><img data-src="https://www.helloimg.com/images/2023/05/02/oqcsL9.png" alt="" width="500px"></p></div><hr><h1 id="the-proof-of-ajcs-theorem"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#the-proof-of-ajcs-theorem">#</a> The Proof of Ajc’s Theorem</h1><h2 id="前置知识梅涅劳斯定理menelaus-theorem"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#前置知识梅涅劳斯定理menelaus-theorem">#</a> 前置知识：梅涅劳斯定理 (Menelaus’ theorem)</h2><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9iYWlrZS5iYWlkdS5jb20vaXRlbS8lRTYlQTIlODUlRTYlQjYlODUlRTUlOEElQjMlRTYlOTYlQUYlRTUlQUUlOUElRTclOTAlODY=">梅涅劳斯定理</span>简称<strong>梅氏定理</strong>，描述了三角形上共线三点带来的比例关系。定理表述及证明如下:</p><details class="info"><summary>梅氏定理</summary><div><p>如图，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">Δ</span></span></span></span>ABC 各边直线上存在<strong> D、F、E</strong> 共线，则</p><p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{FC}{FA}\cdot\frac{EB}{EC}\cdot\frac{DA}{DB}=1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.04633em;vertical-align:-0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.36033em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.04633em;vertical-align:-0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.36033em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-r