"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span></span></p><p>证明:</p><p>过点 C 做直线 CG//DE，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>G</mi><mo>∩</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>G</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">CG \cap DB=G</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∩</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span></span></span></span>.<br> 有:</p><p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>F</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>G</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="1em"></mspace><mfrac><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>G</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace width="1em"></mspace><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>A</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{FC}{FA}=\frac{DG}{DA}\quad \frac{EB}{EC}=\frac{DB}{DG}\quad \frac{DA}{DB}=\frac{DA}{DB}\\  </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.04633em;vertical-align:-0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.36033em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.04633em;vertical-align:-0.686em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nul